  <h2>Live fluid grid example</h2>
  <p>The Bootstrap fluid grid system utilizes <strong>12 columns</strong>, based on a design for a 940px wide container. With responsive CSS enabled, the grid adapts to be 724px and 1170px wide depending on your viewport. Below 767px viewports, the columns stack vertically. The same responsive capabilities, ensuring proper proportions for key screen resolutions and devices. The fluid grid system uses percents instead of traditional pixels for column widths.</p>
