  <h2>Fluid nesting</h2>
  <p>Nesting with fluid grids is a bit different that fixed pixel grids: the number of nested columns should not match the parent's number of columns. Instead, each level of nested columns are reset because each row takes up 100% of the parent column.</p>
  <div class="row-fluid show-grid">
